<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1885,2031]" pageId="3" pageNumber="34">Dorsal-fin origin equidistant from snout tip and caudal-fin origin. Pelvic-fin origin located slightly anterior to vertical through dorsal-fin origin. Anal-fin origin located just behind vertical line through base of posteriormost dorsal-fin rays. Tip of pectoral fin reaching pelvic-fin origin, and tip of pelvic fin reaching anal-fin origin in males and some females.</paragraph>
